Open Ant
Milestone plan
This document describes the work package for each milestone. The set of functionnalities to be delivered with each milestones should be described in another document.


GAME CORE                                                                        GRAPHICS
Milestone 1 : Aboveground                                                        
Move yellow ant around                                                           Set-up minimal GUI
Deal with items (grab,drop,eat)                                                  Display aboveground map
Put scents                                                                       Show aboveground elements
*other outside-related activities should be implemented in this MS*              
                                                                                 
Milestone 2 : Undergound                                                         Show underground map
Digging around and shit                                                          Show underground elements
*other outside-related activities should be implemented in this MS*              
                                                                                 
Milestone 3 : Populate                                                           
Create other kind of ants                                                        Set up sprites for new units
Create other creatures                                                           Set up animations for combat and other events
Write code for creatures' life system (health depletion)                         Set up interface to public game variable: health, caste system, graphics...
Write combat code                                                                
                                                                                 
Milestone 4 : AI                                                                 
Chose a system for the AI - moddable AI would be great.                          
Write basic AI for units - movement, following scents, exchanging food...        









